popular_items.description: Baby, it's cold outside. This Dude should help. We've taken a traditional full-bodied Porter and added just a touch of coconut for a little tropical kick. It's a tasty winter brew that'll warm you up while reminding you that our sunny SoCal summer is just around the corner. Here's to cold beer and warm days, Cheers Dude!.
popular_items.name: Juicebox Series®: Coconut Porter (4-Pack) | 16oz Can | 6.2% abv

popular_items.description:
7 Deadly Sins Series - Pride: Great Grandma's  22oz Bottle.
Way to go, whipper snapper!  You've picked out some top notch hooch!  We took our pride and joy brew, Grandma's Peacan Brown, juiced her up with some molasses and malt, traded out pecans for Madagascar vanilla beans, then aged her in Caribbean rum barrels.  She came out a little older, a little wiser, and a lot more ornery - Like all great grandmas should be.  Here's a toast to generations past.  Cheers Dude!
popular_items.name: 7 Deadly Sins Series - Pride: Great Grandma's

popular_items.description:
Sandbox Series:  Genie  in a Bottle 22oz Bottle.
You're thirsting for something big and bold, well Dude, your wish is our command.  This barrel-aged palate bomb bursts out of the bottle and assaults your senses.  First you'll encounter the adacious mouthfeel of an imperial red ale backed by the sweet undertones of tart cherries.  And just when you think it's over, it hits you hard on the backside - good old American bourbon.  Rub that bottle and see what magic awaits!
popular_items.name: Sandbox Series: Genie in a Bottle

popular_items.description: Orange whip? Orange whip? 3 orange whips.  Here’s a brew that will “a peel” to you! A tantalizing blend of cocoa nib, vanilla bean, and hand-zested California blood orange flavors make this dude semi sweet yet silky smooth. Every sip is bursting with creamy, chocolaty, citrus flavor – and at 6.5 percent alcohol by volume, it’s sure to get your blood pumping. Orange you glad you picked this up!.
popular_items.name: Juicebox Series®: Blood Orange Amber Ale (4-Pack) | 16oz Can | 6.5% abv
